Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9.0.0), libgstreamer-plugins-base0.10-dev, libgstreamer0.10-dev, ros-indigo-actionlib, ros-indigo-actionlib-msgs, ros-indigo-audio-common-msgs, ros-indigo-catkin, ros-indigo-diagnostic-msgs, ros-indigo-message-generation, ros-indigo-roscpp, ros-indigo-roslib
Homepage: http://ros.org/wiki/sound_play
